\id 2PE - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG 2 Peter 01 18/2/91 Macnaughtan 
\h 2 PIDA 
\toc1 Pidamaęž‰ yaapo peao tapaeyeke wapee 
\toc2 2 Pida 
\toc3 2 Pida 
\mt1 Pidamaęž‰ yaapo peao tapaeyeke wapee  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 IĚ±taęž‰ Saimono Pida mo hande Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ make aposolo halimaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Mo hande niki daęž‰taasaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ tikitiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ hone tulaalaęž‰eki halaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hande otaęž‰ seliapo piki ekimaęž‰ handekeeki meleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ do tameiyaęž‰ tapaasome.  
\v 2 Aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make puki lopaęž‰niaasaęž‰eki make otaęž‰ tumbulu baasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ make nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu ipilikaęž‰ honemanu yamaęž‰ ikaęž‰ eki winaęž‰e.   
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wi alaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ maĚ±leke litaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapo  
\p
\v 3 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ welepiki otaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ tikitiki piki hau yaapo mulu polomaęž‰ hau paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me. Do hau manutaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± make epeke hau yaapomaęž‰ niki wi laęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰ hone umaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ molomaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Dupitaęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo laęž‰ ulaęž‰ otaęž‰ aneke make seliapo piki pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu kaęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke. Dupiki pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ ale manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande do kenkenaęž‰ ulaęž‰ hoeyaasaęž‰ puki tiaasaęž‰ hau mea pakaęž‰lao mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ hau paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa apaęž‰taalimikie.  
\v 5 Doeki tekenaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaasemeeki paęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ epeke hau apaęž‰taaluekemaęž‰ honkopu hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa ikaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hau paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hone wilimieki apaęž‰taapaęž‰peke.  
\v 6 Koto ikaęž‰ hone wilimieki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ kone loke hone yaapo lu tumbao haleme hau apaęž‰taapaęž‰peke. Kutupa koto loke hone yaapo lu tumbao halemeeki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ puki hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰pelemeeki apaęž‰taapaęž‰peke. Koto ikaęž‰ puki hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰pelemeeki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau leke pitelemeeki apaęž‰taapaęž‰peke.  
\v 7 Kutupa ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau leke piteleme hau paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kame paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homelemeeki apaęž‰taapaęž‰peke. Kutupa kame paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeleme hau paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homelemeeki apaęž‰taapaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 8 Do seliapo piki hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wia hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ haumanue. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do haumanu mea tumbulu bao wia haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto ale manumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hone witeleme ekitaęž‰ wele putiaasaęž‰ honkopu kilieke.  
\v 9 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ do ekimanu na wia hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ leke otaęž‰ dokaęž‰tiki yaalo hataęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ hoke haumanu tandaęž‰pa paeyawalaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone yonkaęž‰lalaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka kame titio. Mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki wi laa maĚ±leke litaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pa u haenaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ honkopu wopu hao peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaleme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lalimikie.  
\v 11 Dupimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ Paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ na paelo paęž‰laęž‰ Kilu Tombuao halaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamboemenaęž‰ waleke tieke kilieke.   
\p
\v 12 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ meleme otaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ honkopu hao hapaęž‰lia hataęž‰ do alo pimanu ambaęž‰ hone wilimipate IĚ±maęž‰ do hau manutaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ paa opuaaso ombu halueke.  
\v 13 Yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± pa halo anetaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ peaęž‰pekeeki homeketaęž‰ do hau manunaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ wilimi honemanu paa hone u tiatiki pulueke.  
\v 14 Nikaęž‰ hande Tekehali Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao la kiaęž‰ tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do homaęž‰peke loketaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ baalueke hone witolome.  
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± homuluaęž‰ hoki nane make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do haumanu hoto paeyao hone u hamenaęž‰yeke IĚ±maęž‰ honkopu hao potaęž‰manu wepu wialueke.   
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handaęž‰ wilimieki  
\p
\v 16 Mo hande nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ wele paęž‰taęž‰ ipulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ pa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ tameni manunaęž‰ tilao hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ walolo na lomaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ nikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honkopu tieke handomaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Mo hande Kodaęž‰ Apaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki yaapo haleaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ hamono piaęž‰me. Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± wopupiki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Dotaęž‰ ya pukipiki wekie. IĚ±maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu homolome laa pi laęž‰niaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Otaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kone mo pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ epeaęž‰eki opumaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mo hande yako piki potenaęž‰ haomaęž‰ dinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 19 Koto ekinaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ mo hande potopede haliwekimaęž‰ walo haemeke pinaęž‰ hone wopu tulalomaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make koto pi wopu opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ pilimikie. Pa ekipeke koto pitaęž‰ hande lamepamaęž‰ timbaęž‰ leke ale paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peatia pua mo da kaęž‰laęž‰polo hataęž‰ da kaęž‰laęž‰paaso hombulankaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰ nate opolo haenaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laasaęž‰ tupaęž‰e.  
\v 20 Titinaęž‰ pitaęž‰ dupamaęž‰ hone u hapaęž‰peke Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone mo Baibolo paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ teketaęž‰ pa na walaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 21 Pa ekipeke mo laęž‰ wieke pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ halinaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ na epeekepate mo haliwekitaęž‰ Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ handeteke hayekeeki oto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ haleeke tupaęž‰ walao haemekeme.   
\c 2  
\s1 Yayapiki pi walaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki  
\p
\v 1 Makeaaso potopede haliwekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande haemeke wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ opaęž‰liaemeke tupaęž‰ kone yayapiki pi walaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekitaęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ make opaęž‰lialieke. Koto haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ iki hoeyaapeke yayapiki manaęž‰ pimanu mea aęž‰pa make mo hande iki kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalaęž‰ Tekehali hoki walolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone iki hoeyaasaęž‰ haumanu mea ipilimikie.  
\v 2 Kutu pitolo kone wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ yaalaęž‰piki hoke haumanu tolu halimikie. Kutu piteleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ tikitiki piki potaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa hoke haĚ±iĚ± piki pimanu lalimikie.  
\v 3 Do yayapiki pi walaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ pasaęž‰tei pitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ alemanu muluekemaęž‰ makeaaso laęž‰laęž‰ tamenimanu la kilieke. Ametaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kiake kone iki pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ tikitiki yao hataęž‰ iki hoeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ uĚ± na paęž‰elaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 4 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hoke hau pieke enisolo manunaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ pa na minaęž‰paęž‰lae yekepate ikitaęž‰ oni ti uleke paęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao seni pumaęž‰ tonkao timbaęž‰ laęž‰papeke paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ iki pi yokaalu pulu peleme nate yu wia haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 5 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ hoke yenkitaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lae yekepate ipiki hoki walemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikali talaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ minaęž‰ leekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tambaęž‰ mieke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi walo hayeke hali Noa pitaęž‰ mandane watake hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali pea tambaęž‰ miekeme.   
\p
\v 6 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Sodomo Komoto daoni yaapo maĚ±leke lia ti ulekemaęž‰ hoeyaeyeke ekitaęž‰ ipiki hoki walo peleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ waleekeme.  
\v 7 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Loda peteleekeme. Lodataęž‰ epeke hali hataęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mo pi yambelemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ walemeke loke hoeyaasaęž‰ haumanu handolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weleke pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeme.  
\v 8 Koto epeke halitaęž‰ kutupiki wandaęž‰hali ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ hataęž‰ peliolo da kelepolo dupiki temokonaęž‰ hau pimikieki handolo make opitolo hataęž‰ puki tandamaęž‰ homolo tanda tieke mutia peekeme.  
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ hau leke piteleme wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homelemeke paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone ulaęž‰me. Kutupa make mo hoke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ hoke yenki oto paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ mo pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate yu wia haenaęž‰ alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone ulaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Otaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ haĚ±iĚ± piki lokenaęž‰ naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa pinaęž‰maęž‰ hone u haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\p Do yayapikieki walaęž‰laęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homu na piki ikaęž‰ homeke hone u hataęž‰ oli manda halaęž‰ seliapo piki enisolo tititaęž‰ na handomo tiao halememe. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ pa iki kitao halememe.  
\v 11 Mo yayapiki pi waleleme haliweki bepolaake wele wopu piki enisolo haliwekimaęž‰ konetaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ Ikitaęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pelememe laa la la na pu halememe.  
\v 12 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate do haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokemaęž‰ kone iki handeteke haenaęž‰ laa mo honaęž‰maĚ±oĚ± linaęž‰yeke mondu ulaęž‰ tikene halaęž‰ yeti sayalemaęž‰ handelememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki hone wopu na wilimi pimanu kone la la pea hoeyao halememe. Ikitaęž‰ mo tikene halaęž‰ yeti sayale pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ hoeyaalieke.  
\v 13 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tanda piki haumanu peleme ekinaęž‰ iki make koto tupaęž‰ kone tanda piki yenki kilieke.  
\p Ikaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ naęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki tumbaaluekemaęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ hataęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke anemone hau pu halememe. Ikaęž‰ yayapiki potaęž‰ manunaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo hataęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± ne mandakenaęž‰ apaęž‰tao nalemeketaęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ haĚ±iĚ± peao hondo pilake nono pelememe.  
\v 14 Ikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰naęž‰ leke titolo hataęž‰ hoke hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ na pao halememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo damako piki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ honaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea teao halememe. Ikaęž‰taęž‰ pasaęž‰tei pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau puluekemaęž‰ ambaęž‰ mokaęž‰la handa wilimime. Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰eki oto paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ tapake au laa halememe.  
\v 15 Ikitaęž‰ mo hande tikitiki piki potaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao potaęž‰ pomu keaaso hataęž‰ mo hande Bionaęž‰ eiyeke Beilamemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pieke hoke haunaęž‰ mieke mani paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeeke tupaęž‰ koto awili teilememe.  
\v 16 Koto sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰taęž‰ lu pandaęž‰ puniaenaęž‰ mo donkimaęž‰ pi leekeme. Ipikaęž‰ donkimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ leke leekemaęž‰ mo potopedenaęž‰ you hoke haumanu piekeeki saęž‰saęž‰ piekeme.   
\p
\v 17 Do haliwekitaęž‰ mo hande opaęž‰laęž‰ ikali o alaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handelememe. Ikitaęž‰ po tilipumaęž‰ kili mea baalaęž‰ koamaęž‰ handelememe. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ oni timbaęž‰ laęž‰papeke naku tieke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ ambaęž‰ mea wialaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hakoko lia teke na wiki pimanu wepu halememe. Kutupa make mo hokeeki paęž‰taęž‰ haleme wandaęž‰hali pakaęž‰lao poluekemaęž‰ kini piteleme wandaęž‰hali tamuluekemaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ pu halememe.  
\v 19 Ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lu wialaęž‰ hoke hoeyaasaęž‰ haunaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki hataęž‰ kone mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ iki kaęž‰laęž‰paalumeke laa pi laęž‰ u halememe. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi aęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pu halaęž‰ haumaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ minaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ hali halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 20 Wandaęž‰hali epi aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketiso hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ honkopu hake hoke ekimanu pakaęž‰lao kone handeeki manumaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ paa minaęž‰ lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ dupiki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande kini pea haeme tupaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate otaęž‰ ankulake hokeeki paęž‰taęž‰ halememe.  
\v 21 Mo hande yakopiki pi ulaęž‰eki iki paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeeki hone wia kone paa minaęž‰paęž‰lao peleme ekimaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ tikitiki piki ekinaęž‰ potaęž‰ hone na wimikaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ otaęž‰ epolo piaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Ikinaęž‰ pa mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande lo haemeke pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ekie laa dupa walaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\q1 Kikamaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande tolu wieke moku paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ paa laęž‰kaęž‰la pu halaęž‰me  
\m laa make paa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰  
\q1 Mo ikali peiyao ulaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo kenke paęž‰taęž‰ paa peke lulu pu halaęž‰me laa lo halememe.   
\c 3  
\s1 Tekehalinaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Yaka yankeke tonuo. Dotaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ yaka yaapo peao tameiyaęž‰ tapaasome. Do tameiyaęž‰ yaapo telipunaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ hakepiki honemanu mea tialuekemaęž‰yeke do haumanu paa hone u tiaasome.  
\v 2 Yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo yakopiki potopede haliwekimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande la kimi pimanu make hande Paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ pi wiekeeki ikaęž‰ aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ iki kiaęž‰eki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ niminatiki piomenaęž‰ loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 3 Titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la do hone wopu wiaęž‰peke. Mo hande paetolo nate manunaęž‰taęž‰ mandane kitao halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ipilimikie. Koto wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ lelimikie. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki kitaaso hataęž‰ lotaęž‰ pitolo alotaęž‰  
\v 4 Ipikitaęž‰ ipulueke pitaęž‰ na laęž‰ wiekea. Ametaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ handokaęž‰taęž‰pe. Nikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amedataęž‰ ambaęž‰ koto homelemepate pa mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ ambaęž‰ mo hande kenke ya wepitolo wieke tupaęž‰ kone hande mande laa pa do ulaęž‰taa laa lelimikie.  
\v 5 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ kiake pi laęž‰ witolotaęž‰ kenke ya yaapo wepiekeme laęž‰laęž‰ otaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hoki walo halememe. Kenketaęž‰ ikali paęž‰taęž‰ opaęž‰liao ikalimaęž‰taęž‰ kenke au laeyekeme.  
\v 6 Kutupa make mo hande ikali teaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hande ambaęž‰ kenke hoeyaeyekeme.  
\v 7  Koto tupaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande laęž‰ wieke homeke pimaęž‰ kone ame do ulaęž‰ kenke ya yaapotaęž‰ ti ulekemaęž‰ hoeyaenaęž‰yeke amu pea ulaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰ matao haleme wandaęž‰hali pi yokaalu pea hoeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰ nate yu wia haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 8 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate yaka yankeke tonuo. Do alo pi homeke hone na yonkaęž‰lapaęž‰peke. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰taęž‰ nate homeke pitaęž‰ bapi hali tieke eleke eleke manutaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ telipunaęž‰ mandake hau kone paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 9 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ Tekehalitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ kesemaęž‰ pu halaęž‰me lo halememe. Kotoeki na piki ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikinaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo yu wia halaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ hoeyaapaęž‰naęž‰e laataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao ikaęž‰ hoke hau minaęž‰paęž‰laenaęž‰e hone uĚ± halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate Tekehalinaęž‰ Natetaęž‰ mo hande pake nalaęž‰ hali ipulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ipilieke. Koto Natenaęž‰taęž‰ oli yataęž‰ pututu piki eĚ± wi laa alupilieke. Oli yanaęž‰ halaęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ timaęž‰ taa hoeyaotaęž‰ do kenke make kenke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ ale paeyao make taa alupaalieke.  
\v 11-12 Do alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao dupa hoeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰eki yaęž‰leke loaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ekipiki wandaęž‰hali hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Nate epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ditaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kimaaso hataęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± epenaęž‰e laa honkopu hao hapaęž‰peke. Kutu pitolotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ haleme ekitaęž‰ yako pinaęž‰ laa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau leke pu hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo yataęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pao hoeyao mo yanaęž‰ halaęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ mo titipumaęž‰ taa oĚ± laęž‰ palieke.  
\v 13 Pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ mo hande tikitiki hau homeke ulu paęž‰laęž‰ panake kenke ya yaapo epenaęž‰ yu wia halomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka yankeke tonuo. Koto nate yu wia hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hake pea eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na piki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handaa Kodaęž‰ yaapo puki lopaęž‰niao haluekemaęž‰ taapo hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 15 Nikaęž‰ kame seliapo Polomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ haleeke epeke hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki miniki hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ tameiyaęž‰ tapaaso leekeme. Koto tupaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo yu wia halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki miomenaęž‰ waleke wiaaso pitaęž‰laęž‰me hone wopu u hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 16 Polo ipikaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰taęž‰ homeke pi ombu lo halaęž‰me. Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate pi ulaęž‰eki matao hone eleke eleke u haleme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰manu paęž‰taęž‰ koto kone hone wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ mandane pi manutaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ peao walo halememe. Mo mandane Baibolo pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ pu haleme tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo hoeyaasaęž‰eki mea ipu halememe.   
\p
\v 17 Pate iki yaka yankeke tonuo. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koto ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hone wilimime. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ wopu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo lo pi yambolo haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yayapikieki manumaęž‰ iki hatuku pua ikaęž‰ epeke haleme alenaęž‰ mea lopaamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ hone ulaęž‰eki make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ daeyatia pu hapaęž‰peke. Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki ame make wetepe ninaęž‰ make winaęž‰e. Kutu pinaęž‰e.   